Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.94,0:23:39.28,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}辿る空で待っていると
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.28,0:23:40.48,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I meant for you
