Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.97,0:22:46.46,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我祈願與你並肩前行
Comment: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:48.57,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Beautiful it’s beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.98,0:22:53.27,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}正確與否
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.27,0:22:55.62,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}只取決於自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:23:03.49,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}時而莫衷一是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:10.40,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}時而詞不達意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:12.46,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}這也無可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.46,0:23:15.92,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}讓弱小的我變得強大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:21.47,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}是為與你相稱
Comment: 0,0:23:24.41,0:23:25.95,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I ain’t fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.95,0:23:27.95,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我難以割捨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:32.44,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}亦如無法放棄
