Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.70,0:23:44.64,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}直達內心
Comment: 0,0:23:44.64,0:23:45.64,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Mind’s eye flickers
